{"tid":1568103,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實去踩場目的係為咗啲乜?","createTime":"2019-09-14T08:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:10.000Z","uid":180168,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc89b49e74676c64c67591ea01e75a7d16212e58","tid":1568103,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"我地去唱歌, 藍絲狗黎踩場, 佢都會畀人打<br />\n調返轉, 人地去唱歌, 你要去踩場但人又唔夠多, 畀人圍打係正常喎<br />\n<br />\n同埋唱歌咋嘛, 咪由鳩佢地唱<br />\n專登去踩人場係咩心態?<br />\n睇下佢地幾成功, 實有額外佣收啦<br />\n<br />\n遲啲廢老學我地整人鏈, 係咪又要好似啲廢老走去搞學生踩場?"},{"pid":"a3244d61634d05544418227ef33def0b01122f72","tid":1568103,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:21:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da68411a88bc1f12a2f723a123f6a848a1ad70ce","tid":1568103,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"成班得個勇字但蠢過豬西，英雄主義送頭，轟轟烈烈咁輸好撚型？<br />\n應該打既時候唔打<br />\n成堆狗去左淘大保護黑社會，有晒記者拍片，你地就想出去打<br />\n<br />\n藍絲打啲落單既就得<br />\n唔需要硬碰硬<br />\n要10個打1個，唔係1個打10個<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各區接放工，保家衛邨，民間自衛</span></span><br />\n冇ccrv <span style=\"color: red;\">低調</span>先盡興<br />\n<br />\n今晚冇藍絲受傷即係香港人係垃圾"},{"pid":"54c18a5087e759b9f805d971183854d2a8f74ef4","tid":1568103,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"各有各做啦～每個人想法都不同，但最重要係令到自已不被捕！"},{"pid":"fd9954b53f495e5912aee3fc3c9caf361a8e6408","tid":1568103,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n[藍